nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">confidential information</span>&nbsp;and is intended only for the addressee. If you are not the addressee you should not disseminate, distribute or copy this e-mail. Please notify&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"mailto:itsupport@emiratesnfm.ae\" id=\"LPlnk290690\">itsupport@emiratesnfm.ae</a></strong>&nbsp;immediately\r\n by e-mail. If you have received this e-mail by mistake, delete this e-mail from your system. E-mail transmission cannot be guaranteed to be secure or error-free as information could be intercepted, corrupted, lost, destroyed, arrive late or incomplete, or\r\n contain viruses.&nbsp;EnFM therefore does not accept liability for any errors or omissions in the contents of this message, which arise as a result of e-mail transmission. If verification is required, please request a hard copy version.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '2025-09-11 13:03:11', '[{\"name\":\"image001.png\",\"size\":138478,\"mime\":\"image\\/png\"}]', '2025-09-25 04:53:04', '2025-09-27 03:39:38'),
(6, 1, 'noreply@zoho.com', 'ZohoMail - New login activity', '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\"><html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><head>  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />  <title>Account Access Notification</title></head><body><div style=\"width:600px; margin:0 auto; border:1px solid #ddd; overflow:hidden; font:14px/20px \'Trebuchet MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background-color:#fcfcfc;\">	<div style=\"height:auto; padding:24px 0 0 20px;\">    	<a href=\"https://www.zoho.com/mail\"><img style=\"border:none;\" height=\"48\" src=\"https://www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/images/productlogos/mail.png\" title=\"Zoho Mail\" /></a>    </div>        <div style=\"margin:25px 20px 15px; padding:0px;\">      Dear Quality Services,        <br />        <p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 50px;\">Your account info@q-iso.ae was recently accessed via SMTP. The Time, IP and location details of the activity are available below:</p>        <br />        <div align=\"center\">        <table cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" bordercolor=\"#aaa\" style=\"margin:5px 0 0 0; font-size:13px;\">          <tr><th style=\'text-align: left;width: 20%;\'>TIME</th><td>Fri Sep 12 14:11:07 GST 2025</td><tr><tr><th style=\'text-align: left;\'>IP</th><td>154.192.9.44</td><tr><tr><th style=\'text-align: left;\'>LOCATION</th><td>Islamabad, PK</td><tr>        </table>        </div>        <br />        <p style=\"text-align:justify\">In case the above information appears appropriate, you can ignore this email.</p>        <p style=\"text-align:justify\">If you have not used your account or sent any email in the above time, we highly recommend you to <a style=\'color:#1a80cf;\' href=\'https://www.zoho.com/mail/help/adminconsole/password-reset.html#alink2\'>change the password</a> and <a style=\'color:#1a80cf;\' href=\'https://www.zoho.com/mail/help/adminconsole/two-factor-authentication.html\'>enable TFA</a> for the account to make it more secure in future.</p>        <br />        <p style=\"text-align:justify\">Feel free to write to <a style=\"color:#1a80cf;\" href=\"mailto:support@zohomail.com\">support@zohomail.com</a>, for further clarifications.</p>		Thanks!<br />        ZohoMail Services<br /><br />        <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Note:</b> The location provided in the email is based on the IP address and may vary from your actual location in case you use a VPN or other proxy networks. In case your public IP matches with the above IP you may ignore this email. Contact your network administrator to know your public IP.</p>    </div></div></body></html>', '2025-09-12 03:11:08', '[]', '2025-09-25 04:53:04', '2025-09-27 03:39:38');
